      "embed_id": "48e25bb8-a608-45e8-9671-cdbf3e93dec9",
      "type": "event",
      "content": "type: event_result\nid: \"314828340\"\nprovider: meetup\ntitle: Use AI and WiFi to Build Income Online\ndescription: \"AI has opened the door to new online business models.\\nSometimes, all it takes to get started is AI, WiFi, and a clear plan.\\n\\nIn this free live workshop, Paul Chuter will share a clear and structured approach to getting started with an online business using AI.\\n\\n📌Important : After clicking “Attend” on Meetup, please complete your regitration using the webinar registration link shown on the event page.\\n\\n**What we’ll cover**\\n\\\\- A step\\\\-by\\\\-step introduction to building an online income stream with AI\\n\\\\- Different business models that can fit different goals\\\\, lifestyles\\\\, and schedules\\n\\\\- How to create a simple action plan you can apply after the session\\n\\\\- Ways to move faster by using practical tools instead of overcomplicating the process How to build momentum online with more clarity in 2026\\n\\n**Who should attend**\\nThis session is a good fit for:\\n\\\\- Beginners who want to start something online\\n\\\\- People looking for a side hustle or additional income stream\\n\\\\- Those who want a more flexible way of working\\n\\\\- Anyone curious about using AI to simplify the path into online business\\n\\n**Why join**\\nIf you want to explore online income opportunities without getting buried in technical complexity, this webinar will give you a more concrete starting point and help you see what could fit you best.\\n\\nPlaces are limited, so reserve your spot early using the registration link on the event page.\\n\\nDisclaimer: This group and its events follow Meetup’s policies, guidelines, and terms of service. We make no guarantees or promises of results and do not provide financial, legal, investment, or medical advice. All content is shared for educational and community purposes only. All webinars are free to attend, and no purchase is required\"\nurl: \"https://www.meetup.com/berlin-freedom-growth-netw/events/314828340/\"\ndate_start: \"2026-05-25T21:00:00+02:00\"\ndate_end: \"2026-05-25T22:30:00+02:00\"\ntimezone: Europe/Berlin\nevent_type: ONLINE\nvenue_name: Online event\nvenue_address: \"\"\nvenue_city: \"\"\nvenue_state: \"\"\nvenue_country: \"\"\nvenue_lat: -8.521147\nvenue_lon: 179.1962\norganizer_id: \"38496869\"\norganizer_name: Berlin - Freedom & Growth Network\norganizer_slug: berlin-freedom-growth-netw\nrsvp_count: 1\nis_paid: false\nfee: null\nimage_url: \"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/8/2/4/1/highres_534273345.jpeg\"\nhash: 37ea3ef9f228b9d2\nembed_ref: use-ai-and-YnF\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
