      "embed_id": "4ab09653-fe97-46c4-a237-7728bfd50959",
      "type": "event",
      "content": "type: event_result\nid: \"2345934\"\nprovider: resident_advisor\ntitle: HEISSS x Mitmischen I 40 hours\ndescription: \"RA Pick: A 40-hour session in Else? Summer starts here.\\nLineup: abs8lute, BBetriebswirt, Disguised, DJ MARIA., Josiane, Juri Heidemann, Newa, THC, VIL (PT), CRAVO\\nGenres: Techno, House\\nDamn you really don’t want to miss this one...\\n\\nHEISSS x MITMISCHEN @ else  \\n24.05.2026 — 26.05.2026  \\n40 hours straight.\\n\\n5€ re-entry \\n(also for guestlist) \\n\\nwe’re going all in, sunday till tuesday with amazing artists and showcases by our favorite local collectives. \\n\\ncome for one drink… you know how it ends.\\n\\nmark the date, come early, stay forever.\\n\\n_\\n\\nWhere is Else?\\nIn the heart of East Berlin, right beside Treptower Park SBahn Station.\\n\\nWhat if it rains?\\nElse's entire open-air dancefloor is covered by a transparent roof that will keep you warm and dry.\\n\\nWhat's the sound system?\\nThere's a brand new, high-end sound system: Lambda Labs QX3 and a new DJ booth, which is surrounded by the crowd from all sides.\\n\\nWhen does the indoor room open?\\nAfter 22:00 'til the early hours.\\n\\nIs there food?\\nOven-baked pizza all-day.\\n\\nIs there a chill-out space?\\nHang out and have a drink at our riverside terrace.\\n\\nWhat's the minimum age for entry?\\n21+\\n\\nDo you take cash or card?\\n- CASH only at the door\\n- CARD only at the bars\\n\\nWhere can I buy a ticket?\\nTickets are available on RA or at the door with a CASH payment only.\\n\\nRA ticket does not guarantee entry; purchased tickets will be refunded in that case.\"\nurl: \"https://ra.co/events/2345934\"\ndate_start: \"2026-05-24T14:00:00.000\"\ndate_end: \"2026-05-26T06:00:00.000\"\ntimezone: null\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: Else\nvenue_address: \"An den Treptowers 10, 12435 Berlin\"\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: null\nvenue_country: null\nvenue_lat: 52.494739\nvenue_lon: 13.462161\norganizer_name: Else Events\norganizer_slug: null\norganizer_id: null\nrsvp_count: 2668\nis_paid: true\nfee: null\nimage_url: \"https://images.ra.co/d365876b2c76a09dc88ef29da95addc96bbd4475.jpg\"\nartists: abs8lute|BBetriebswirt|Disguised|DJ MARIA.|Josiane|Juri Heidemann|Newa|THC|VIL (PT)|CRAVO\ngenres: Techno|House\nminimum_age: 21\nis_festival: false\nhash: 06ecbf1980bdb5e5\nembed_ref: heisss-x-mitmischen-pHM\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
