      "content": "type: event_result\nid: \"2449291\"\nprovider: resident_advisor\ntitle: \"MOM'S MINI DISCO — A FAMILY DAYTIME DISCO WITH POP-UP WINE BAR, OYSTERS & SNACKS\"\ndescription: \"Lineup: Lilly & Kazan, Frivolous\\nGenres: Disco\\nA daytime dancefloor for kids, families & grown-up groove lovers.\\nNatural wines, oyster bar, delicious snacks, little dancers & sunny Sunday energy all under one roof.\\n\\n- Pop-Up wine bar by Pamuk Wines\\n- Oyster bar & snacks by Dinner Squats\\n- Kid-friendly drinks & family vibes\\n- Feel-good grooves all day by Gingerblack, Önder Pamuk, Frivolous & Friends\\n\\n14:00 — 22:00\\n\\nKids are welcome. Cute parents too.\"\nurl: \"https://ra.co/events/2449291\"\ndate_start: \"2026-05-24T14:00:00.000\"\ndate_end: \"2026-05-25T22:00:00.000\"\ntimezone: null\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: Mom's Limousine Service\nvenue_address: \"Georgenstrasse 184, 10117 Berlin\"\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: null\nvenue_country: null\nvenue_lat: 52.52\nvenue_lon: 13.39\norganizer_name: Mom's Limousine Service\norganizer_slug: null\norganizer_id: null\nrsvp_count: 7\nis_paid: false\nfee: null\nimage_url: \"https://images.ra.co/6eb562bb9bd2627945136bbe9d8d509f98045927.jpg\"\nartists: Lilly & Kazan|Frivolous\ngenres: Disco\nminimum_age: null\nis_festival: false\nhash: 8e0a871ee4f216f5\nembed_ref: mom-s-mini-0Mk\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
