      "embed_id": "44c9ba6e-8af4-482e-82e2-d5a3cf75d91e",
      "type": "event",
      "content": "type: event_result\nid: \"2430278\"\nprovider: resident_advisor\ntitle: Body Language - long weekend closing\ndescription: \"RA Pick: Monday off: Body Language on! Head to Kreuzwerk to close the long weekend with a deep dive into house, courtesy of Stella Zekri, Maryisonacid, Rose Kourts and more.\\nLineup: Camilla Rae, Maryisonacid, Rose Kourts, Stella Zekri, Twist Fire\\nGenres: House\\nYou’re invited to the next dance on Monday 25.05\\n\\nIt’s already a public holiday but take the Tuesday off too diva, you deserve it! \\n\\nThis time round we'll be at Kreuzwerk - but we'll be keeping it cute as always, only using the gorj Greenhouse Floor and deck area. Limited capacity, maximum love! \\n\\nOpen 15-01 for the dancers with a curfew xoxo\\n\"\nurl: \"https://ra.co/events/2430278\"\ndate_start: \"2026-05-25T15:00:00.000\"\ndate_end: \"2026-05-26T01:00:00.000\"\ntimezone: null\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: KREUZWERK\nvenue_address: \"Lobeckstraße 30-35, 10969 Berlin, Deutschland\"\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: null\nvenue_country: null\nvenue_lat: 53\nvenue_lon: 13\norganizer_name: Body Language\norganizer_slug: null\norganizer_id: null\nrsvp_count: 65\nis_paid: true\nfee_amount: \"22\"\nfee_currency: EUR\nimage_url: \"https://images.ra.co/1a52cacbd48c22b5b4ef45cac017ff4717af89eb.jpg\"\nartists: Camilla Rae|Maryisonacid|Rose Kourts|Stella Zekri|Twist Fire\ngenres: House\nminimum_age: 21\nis_festival: false\nhash: b16a3316047dd929\nembed_ref: body-language-long-05g\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
