      "content": "type: event_result\nid: \"2428568\"\nprovider: resident_advisor\ntitle: Mutual Attraction\ndescription: \"RA Pick: Mutual Attraction provides the perfect bounce for daytime house lovers ready to bop to strictly local sounds.\\nLineup: E Molina, Magic of the Groove, Jacob Meehan\\nGenres: House, Disco\\nMutual Attraction Vol. 2 descends once again onto Crack Bellmer for the dreamiest of daytime ki’s. \\nSounds to wiggle to by Jacob Meehan (Buttons) and the MA residents.\\nIt’s a holigay and we’ll have a frozen drink surprise, so come thirsty!\"\nurl: \"https://ra.co/events/2428568\"\ndate_start: \"2026-05-25T15:00:00.000\"\ndate_end: \"2026-05-25T23:59:00.000\"\ntimezone: null\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: Crack Bellmer\nvenue_address: Revaler Strasse 99; 10245 Berlin-Friedrichshain; Berlin; Germany\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: null\nvenue_country: null\nvenue_lat: 52.507714\nvenue_lon: 13.454258\norganizer: null\nrsvp_count: 12\nis_paid: false\nfee: null\nimage_url: \"https://images.ra.co/2b15b5dc52f41b6b4f81db3c8cea50f3a25c7242.png\"\nartists: E Molina|Magic of the Groove|Jacob Meehan\ngenres: House|Disco\nminimum_age: 21\nis_festival: false\nhash: 676e87af1ab378a5\nembed_ref: mutual-attraction-iQh\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
