      "embed_id": "f3fd89b7-444c-4528-90fe-f9017f195546",
      "type": "event",
      "content": "type: event_result\nid: \"2378314\"\nprovider: resident_advisor\ntitle: infinite bisous + Naran Ratan Ensemble Plays the Music of Naran Ratan\ndescription: \"Genres: Ambient\\ninfinite bisous\\ninfinite bisous returns from hermetic isolation to release his 4th album, épi in Spring 2026. \\n\\nRory McCarthy is an Irish-English Producer, Multi-Instrumentalist (Connan Mockasin, Mac DeMarco, Beck…) and co-founder of elusive Internet Collective, tasty morsels (morsels.website), whose intimate releases have seen praise from the likes of Ryuichi Sakamoto, Iggy Pop, Oneohtrix Point Never and beyond. \\n\\nNaran Ratan\\nNaran Ratan is the composer for the casio cz synthesizer series. The Naran Ratan Ensemble Plays the Music of Naran Ratan.\"\nurl: \"https://ra.co/events/2378314\"\ndate_start: \"2026-05-25T20:00:00.000\"\ndate_end: \"2026-05-25T22:00:00.000\"\ntimezone: null\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: Silent Green\nvenue_address: \"Gerichtstraße 35, 13347 Berlin, Germany\"\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: null\nvenue_country: null\nvenue_lat: 52.544997\nvenue_lon: 13.366558\norganizer: null\nrsvp_count: 3\nis_paid: true\nfee_amount: 19.20€\nfee_currency: EUR\nimage_url: \"https://images.ra.co/be1af6d4482e4f1190f32e88159a7ab24694ff88.png\"\nartists: null\ngenres: Ambient\nminimum_age: 18\nis_festival: false\nhash: 71bbc69f7f61ff0f\nembed_ref: infinite-bisous-naran-qyB\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
