      "content": "type: event_result\nid: \"2423406\"\nprovider: resident_advisor\ntitle: ◥◣SINGULARITY◥◣\ndescription: \"Lineup: Bours?, Inverse Element, Skungal, PHLOXO\\nGenres: Techno\\n* community tickets * are available in limited quantities for people who are unemployed, receiving social welfare, for holders of a severely disabled persons card, and for recipients under the asylum seekers benefits act. Students do not de facto qualify for this discount, which is generally aimed at giving access to cultural events and other services to people receiving social assistance. Door staff might request the presentation of relevant identification with your presale ticket when entering the venue.\\n\"\nurl: \"https://ra.co/events/2423406\"\ndate_start: \"2026-05-25T23:00:00.000\"\ndate_end: \"2026-05-26T08:00:00.000\"\ntimezone: null\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: Tresor / Globus\nvenue_address: Köpenickerstrasse 70; Mitte; 10179 Berlin; Germany\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: null\nvenue_country: null\nvenue_lat: 52.51088\nvenue_lon: 13.4201\norganizer_name: Tresor Club\norganizer_slug: null\norganizer_id: null\nrsvp_count: 270\nis_paid: true\nfee: null\nimage_url: \"https://images.ra.co/fd20737f2264f7b8baf0c251e83443b4517e333f.png\"\nartists: Bours?|Inverse Element|Skungal|PHLOXO\ngenres: Techno\nminimum_age: null\nis_festival: false\nhash: 64d159591f919c91\nembed_ref: singularity-p3g\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
