      "type": "event",
      "content": "type: event_result\nid: \"2450706\"\nprovider: resident_advisor\ntitle: Klittag - Open Air Tiki Dayparty\ndescription: \"Genres: Experimental, Acid\\nHast du deine Bikini? Well...we'll see about that. Bring it along to Klittag, Berlin's infamous open air daytime tiki party, you'll need it! (One bikini must be handed in at the gate for entry and will only be returned upon a unanimous vote by the DJs and promoter).\\n\\nKick back on the asphalt and enjoy our large, burning man style bonfire, sauna, multiple charcoal pit grilling stations (bring your own meat, meat will not be provided), and of course TIKI TORCHES! If you've never been to Magaluf, DJ Clit Edging will bring the island experience right to ya here in Berlin on site! You better not miss this time!\\n\\nEveryone in attendance must film AND POST at least one instagram reel that includes multiple emojis. Camera rolls will be checked upon exit (and entry too, fuck it, just to see if you have anything interesting).\\n\\nThings which will not be allowed in the space:\\n-sunglasses\\n-beach towels or blankets of any kind\\n-flip flops or any type of footwear that covers the soles of the feet\\n-any type of UV protection whatsoever other than sheer genetic willpower. THIS MEANS: no sunblock, sunscreen, tanning oil (you will be sniffed by a canine unit and swiped with a white satin glove at the gate), umbrellas, hats, coverups, fuckin...what are those things called...sarongs? Doesnt matter i'll know it when i see it.\\n-cooling instruments such as fans, ice, water, or any type of spray bottle (no matter how caustic its contents. there is no argument to be made.)\\n-physically fit and/or good looking people (we had enough of those motherfuckers at Klitnacht)\\n-Piña Coladas (this policy will be VERY strictly enforced by the ordnungstadtpolizei or however you pronounce it, who have been invited to erect an inspection box next to the unisex urinal trough and to provide plainbikini officers to intermingle with guests and interdict any illicit trinkmixes).\\n\\n-everyone must smoke at LEAST one cigarette at the door as part of the entry evaluation. And a real one, no slims or lights or whatever t...\"\nurl: \"https://ra.co/events/2450706\"\ndate_start: \"2026-05-26T05:00:00.000\"\ndate_end: \"2026-05-26T21:30:00.000\"\ntimezone: null\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: TBA - Groucho-Marx-Alleestraßebanhof\nvenue_address: null\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: null\nvenue_country: null\nvenue_lat: 0\nvenue_lon: 0\norganizer_name: DJ Clit Edging\norganizer_slug: null\norganizer_id: null\nrsvp_count: 3\nis_paid: true\nfee_amount: \"0\"\nfee_currency: EUR\nimage_url: null\nartists: null\ngenres: Experimental|Acid\nminimum_age: 18\nis_festival: false\nhash: 6e7e6b9881220b2d\nembed_ref: klittag-open-air-aqK\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
