      "content": "type: event_result\nid: \"314524322\"\nprovider: meetup\ntitle: AI Agent Builders Berlin powered by Dataiku\ndescription: \"**Berlin, let’s talk agents. 🚀**\\nWe’re bringing the local AI community together for another evening focused on the fast-evolving world of **generative AI and autonomous agents** — and how teams are turning them into practical, scalable solutions.\\n\\nThe meetup will feature a short session on what it really takes to **operationalize AI agents**: from design and deployment to oversight, orchestration, and management in production environments. After that, the floor is yours — with plenty of time to meet other builders, exchange perspectives, and continue the conversation over food and drinks.\\n\\n**What to expect:**\\n🎤 A featured talk on building and managing AI agents in practice\\n👀 A closer look through live demos\\n🤝 Informal networking with AI practitioners, builders, and innovators\\n🍻 Discussions with the Berlin data & AI community over drinks and pizza\\n\\nWhether you’re already experimenting with multi-agent systems or just starting to explore the space, this meetup is a chance to hear how others are approaching the challenge, share ideas, and connect with peers in Berlin.\"\nurl: \"https://www.meetup.com/ai-agent-builders-berlin-by-dataiku/events/314524322/\"\ndate_start: \"2026-05-27T18:00:00+02:00\"\ndate_end: \"2026-05-27T21:00:00+02:00\"\ntimezone: Europe/Berlin\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: Panorama Hub betahaus | MORITZPLATZ\nvenue_address: Lobeckstr 30-35\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: \"\"\nvenue_country: de\nvenue_lat: 52.502872\nvenue_lon: 13.407759\norganizer_id: \"26070166\"\norganizer_name: AI Agent Builders Berlin powered by Dataiku\norganizer_slug: ai-agent-builders-berlin-by-dataiku\nrsvp_count: 96\nis_paid: false\nfee: null\nimage_url: \"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/3/8/6/6/highres_533954438.jpeg\"\nhash: d1c8cb8c38b27135\nembed_ref: ai-agent-builders-zGu\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
