      "embed_id": "17c43cf3-ae70-48d7-a8ed-e58537f19e11",
      "type": "event",
      "content": "type: event_result\nid: \"2434080\"\nprovider: resident_advisor\ntitle: Klubkneipe x Tuesday Ritual - Bodypaint Photoshoot Workshop\ndescription: \"Lineup: Charlotte Lion, DJoy, Sinetiketa\\nGenres: House, Tech House\\nTuesday Ritual x Klub Kneipe\\nhosted by Caos Collective\\n\\nThis week features a Bodypaint Photoshoot Workshop — a creative space to explore the body as a canvas through color, texture and expression.\\n\\nParticipants are invited to experiment with body painting and take part in a collaborative photoshoot in a relaxed, open atmosphere.\\n\\nAlongside, music creates a soft and immersive setting throughout the evening.\\n\\nCome by to create, observe or simply spend time together.\\n\\n6 PM – 2 AM\"\nurl: \"https://ra.co/events/2434080\"\ndate_start: \"2026-05-26T18:00:00.000\"\ndate_end: \"2026-05-27T02:00:00.000\"\ntimezone: null\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: Prisma\nvenue_address: \"Brückenstraße 1, 10179 Berlin\"\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: null\nvenue_country: null\nvenue_lat: 52.51\nvenue_lon: 13.42\norganizer: null\nrsvp_count: 3\nis_paid: true\nfee_amount: \"0\"\nfee_currency: EUR\nimage_url: \"https://images.ra.co/83583e4d6ac2596baf0230a1774c8ab85069e642.png\"\nartists: Charlotte Lion|DJoy|Sinetiketa\ngenres: House|Tech House\nminimum_age: 18\nis_festival: false\nhash: 11af12ccb4cc6c34\nembed_ref: klubkneipe-x-tuesday-M8X\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
