      "embed_id": "06debb1b-2e6d-4385-80db-b6eadad46f7d",
      "type": "event",
      "content": "type: event_result\nid: \"314313690\"\nprovider: meetup\ntitle: \"Build Smarter AI: GraphRAG & Generative AI Workshop\"\ndescription: \"Register: https://www.eventbrite.de/e/build-smarter-ai-graphrag-generative-ai-workshop-tickets-1985345958205\\n\\nJoin us for a hands-on introduction to Generative AI with Neo4j at 42 Berlin.\\n**Large language models are powerful — but without structure, they lose context fast.**\\n**As part of the mAI ist für AI series at 42 Berlin, this workshop explores how [Neo4j](https://neo4j.com/ \\\"https://neo4j.com/\\\") can improve GenAI applications and reduce common challenges such as hallucinations.**\\nIn this instructor-led workshop, participants will explore how graph databases can improve GenAI applications and reduce common challenges such as hallucinations. You’ll learn key concepts including Large Language Models (LLMs), Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG), GraphRAG, vector search, knowledge graphs, and AI agents.\\nThe workshop follows a **mixed format, combining short theoretical inputs with practical exercises**. Participants will work through tasks while instructors are available to support and answer questions.\"\nurl: \"https://www.meetup.com/graphdb-dach/events/314313690/\"\ndate_start: \"2026-05-27T16:00:00+02:00\"\ndate_end: \"2026-05-27T19:00:00+02:00\"\ntimezone: Europe/Berlin\nevent_type: PHYSICAL\nvenue_name: 42 Berlin Coding School\nvenue_address: \"Harzer Straße 42, 12059 Berlin,\"\nvenue_city: Berlin\nvenue_state: \"\"\nvenue_country: DE\nvenue_lat: 52.484417\nvenue_lon: 13.44976\norganizer_id: \"1954181\"\norganizer_name: \"Graph Database - DACH (Germany, Austria, Switzerland )\"\norganizer_slug: graphdb-dach\nrsvp_count: 18\nis_paid: false\nfee: null\nimage_url: \"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/8/2/a/5/highres_533733445.jpeg\"\nhash: ad43fc587ccb73cf\nembed_ref: build-smarter-ai-q2J\napp_id: events\nskill_id: search",
      "parent_embed_id": "15c08e13-c6c5-4c0c-a10a-1880bee5450a",
      "embed_ids": null
